<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>远足 on DaDa</title><link>https://example.org/tags/%E8%BF%9C%E8%B6%B3/</link><description>Recent content in 远足 on DaDa</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en-us</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 11:10:00 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://example.org/tags/%E8%BF%9C%E8%B6%B3/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>Amazon 徒步背包推荐：登山、远足和轻装出行的核心装备</title><link>https://example.org/posts/amazon-hiking-backpack-guide/</link><pubDate>Sat, 20 Jun 2026 11:10:00 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://example.org/posts/amazon-hiking-backpack-guide/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;徒步背包是户外出行里最重要的功能性装备之一。真正专业的背包，决定因素不只是“能装多少”，还包括背负系统是否合理、肩带和腰带是否分散压力、背部是否透气，以及分仓设计能否让补给和装备快速取用。对于徒步、远足和轻量登山，背包的舒适度直接影响整条线路的体验。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>